%matplotlib inline
from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
x = np.linspace(0, 1, 100)
y = 0.2+0.4*x**2+0.3*x*np.sin(15*x)+0.05*np.cos(50*x)
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.plot(x, y)

from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
%matplotlib widget
x = np.linspace(0, 1, 100)
y = 0.2+0.4*x**2+0.3*x*np.sin(15*x)+0.05*np.cos(50*x)
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.plot(x, y)
